{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235090/extras/Miri.png?t=1587248383\" /><br><strong>Magical Miri</strong> is a <strong>2D side scroller platform video game in anime style</strong> and with a little <strong>fan service</strong>. It tells the story of Miri, a magic apprentice who is trying to prevent a possible war between dimensions. To achieve it, she must travel to 5 different kingdoms to beat the most powerful sorceresses and get their magic crystals that will grant her access to the Supreme Academy of Magic, where she\u2019ll find a big surprise.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235090/extras/STUDIO_ROXIS_LOGO.png?t=1587248383\" /><br><strong>Estudio Roxis</strong> is a company of two guys having fun creating video games.<br>As gamers and anime followers, we wanted to create a video game with an <strong>anime style, good gameplay, NES difficulty style level, fun to play, catchy soundtrack and endearing characters.</strong><br>Inspired by classics like <strong>Ghost 'n Goblins, Castlevania, and Mega Man</strong>, here is what we've achieved, <strong>we hope you enjoy playing it as we enjoyed creating it.</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235090/extras/YI0rJI.gif?t=1587248383\" />\u2001\u2001\u2001<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235090/extras/YI0rJI.gif?t=1587248383\" />\u2001\u2001\u2001<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235090/extras/YI0rJI.gif?t=1587248383\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Full controller support.<br></li><li>All original characters and art.<br></li><li>A powerful original sound track.<br></li><li>Non linear progression.<br></li><li>25+ different enemi